对！就如我刚刚在想
Just what I was thinkin'. A trio of trespassers!

402
00:20:11,670 --> 00:20:14,006
三个违规的家伙
And quite by accident, let me assure you.

403
00:20:12,126 --> 00:20:13,354
这完全是个意外！

404
00:20:14,047 --> 00:20:15,924
我跟你们保证 这只是航行上的小小的错误
A simple navigational error.

405
00:20:15,966 --> 00:20:17,926
等等...
Whoa, whoa, wait, wait, wait.

406
00:20:17,968 --> 00:20:21,930
我认识你 你是木法沙的小跟班
I know you. You're Mufasa's little stooge.

407
00:20:21,972 --> 00:20:24,308
夫人 我是国王陛下的总管
I, madam, am the king's major-domo.

408
00:20:24,349 --> 00:20:27,436
这么说你就是...
- And that would make you... - The future king.

409
00:20:27,477 --> 00:20:31,064
未来的国王
Do you know what we do to kings who step out of their kingdom?

410
00:20:28,009 --> 00:20:32,309
你知道我们是怎么对付 超出自己国界的国王吗？

411
00:20:31,106 --> 00:20:33,483
你们也不能把我怎么样啊！
You can't do anything to me.

412
00:20:33,483 --> 00:20:34,943
理论上可以 我们在他们的土地上
Technically, they can.

413
00:20:34,985 --> 00:20:36,278
We are on their land.

414
00:20:36,320 --> 00:20:38,197
可是沙祖你跟我说 他们只是爱流口水的傻瓜啊！
But, Zazu, you told me they're nothin'...

415
00:20:38,238 --> 00:20:40,616
but slobbering, mangy, stupid poachers.

416
00:20:40,657 --> 00:20:42,242
能不能不要再提 傻瓜这两个字？
Lx-nay on the upid-stay.

417
00:20:42,284 --> 00:20:44,161
嘿！你叫谁是傻瓜？
Who are you callin' upid-stay?

418
00:20:44,161 --> 00:20:46,413
停...你看那个太阳 我该走了
My, my, my. Look at the sun! It's time to go!

419
00:20:46,455 --> 00:20:47,623
急什么？ 我们很乐意你留下来晚餐
What's the hurry?

420
00:20:47,664 --> 00:20:49,625
We'd love you to stick around for dinner.

421
00:20:49,666 --> 00:20:53,086
是呀...
Yeah, we could have whatever's... lion around!

422
00:20:51,132 --> 00:20:53,532
我们可以吃... 狮子大餐呀！

423
00:20:53,170 --> 00:20:55,130
哈...
Wait, wait, wait, I got one, I got one!

424
00:20:55,172 --> 00:20:58,050
等等... 有了，有了，有了
Make mine a cub sandwich! What'd you think?

425
00:20:55,970 --> 00:20:58,302
我要一份幼狮三明治 你觉得呢？

426
00:20:58,472 --> 00:21:00,372
哈...

427
00:21:00,844 --> 00:21:02,554
什么？阿德？
What, Ed? What is it?

428
00:21:02,596 --> 00:21:04,389
什么？
Hey, did we order this dinner to go?

429
00:21:04,431 --> 00:21:05,599
我们订的晚餐要外带吗？
No, why?

430
00:21:05,641 --> 00:21:07,893
没有啊！怎么啦？
'Cause there it goes!

431
00:21:06,581 --> 00:21:09,675
因为他们跑了

432
00:21:14,066 --> 00:21:15,234
我们甩掉他们了吗？
Did we lose 'em?

433
00:21:15,275 --> 00:21:18,320
我想是的
I think so. Where's Zazu?

434
00:21:18,362 --> 00:21:20,531
沙祖在哪？
The little major-domo bird hippety-hopped...

435
00:21:18,759 --> 00:21:23,526
原来我们的小总管 一路赶着想做只白煮鸟

436
00:21:20,572 --> 00:21:22,658
all the way to the birdie-boiler.

437
00:21:22,699 --> 00:21:25,452
不！我不要做白煮鸟！
Oh, no! Not the birdie-boiler!

438
00:21:29,206 --> 00:21:32,376
嘿！你们为什么不去找一个 跟你们差不多大的
Hey, why don't you pick on somebody your own size?

439
00:21:32,417 --> 00:21:34,711
像...你吗？
- Like you? - Oops.

440
00:21:34,141 --> 00:21:36,132
哦哦！

441
00:21:50,853 --> 00:21:52,729
辛巴
Simba!

442
00:22:10,914 --> 00:22:14,293
快来呀！小宝贝
Here, kitty, kitty, kitty.

443
00:22:18,213 --> 00:22:19,631
哈哈...就这样吗？
Heh! That was it?

444
00:22:20,924 --> 00:22:22,634
再吼一次，来呀！
Do it again. Come on.

445
00:22:34,605 --> 00:22:36,148
大...大哥
Oh, please, please! Uncle, uncle!

446
00:22:36,190 --> 00:22:38,525
误会...误会
- Silence! - We're gonna shut up right now!

447
00:22:36,904 --> 00:22:37,598
闭嘴！

448
00:22:38,567 --> 00:22:40,319
闭嘴！我们都闭嘴
Calm down. We're really sorry.

449
00:22:40,360 --> 00:22:43,780
别激动
If you ever come near my son again...

450
00:22:39,607 --> 00:22:40,596
我们真的很抱歉

451
00:22:40,741 --> 00:22:44,040
如果你们敢再靠近我儿子

452
00:22:43,780 --> 00:22:45,407
这位...这位是您的...
Oh, this is your son?

453
00:22:45,449 --> 00:22:47,701
哦！是您的公子啊
- Oh, your son? - Did you know that?

454
00:22:47,743 --> 00:22:50,204
你知道吗？
No. Me? I didn't know... No, did you?

455
00:22:48,215 --> 00:22:49,239
不，我不知道

456
00:22:50,245 --> 00:22:52,122
这个... 你...你知道吗？
- No, of course not. - No.

457
00:22:52,164 --> 00:22:53,373
不，当然不知道
- Ed? - Ed?

458
00:22:52,286 --> 00:22:55,187
不！阿德？

459
00:22:56,627 --> 00:22:57,961
溜
Toodles.

460
00:23:05,010 --> 00:23:06,303
爸，我...
Dad, I...

461
00:23:06,345 --> 00:23:08,138
你故意违抗我的命令
You deliberately disobeyed me.

462
00:23:09,306 --> 00:23:10,849
爸，我很抱歉
Dad, I'm sorry.

463
00:23:10,891 --> 00:23:12,226
跟我回家去
Let's go home.

464
00:23:14,853 --> 00:23:17,481
我认为你非常勇敢
I thought you were very brave.

465
00:23:34,206 --> 00:23:35,707
沙祖
Zazu.

466
00:23:37,793 --> 00:23:40,671
是的，陛下
- Yes, sire? - Take Nala home.

467
00:23:40,671 --> 00:23:43,674
带娜娜回家
I've got to teach my son a lesson.

468
00:23:41,202 --> 00:23:44,797
我必须要给我儿子上一课

469
00:23:47,845 --> 00:23:49,805
娜娜，走吧
Come, Nala.

470
00:23:49,847 --> 00:23:51,223
辛巴，唉！
Simba...

471
00:23:51,265 --> 00:23:53,267
祝你好运
Good luck.

472
00:23:58,689 --> 00:24:00,649
辛巴
Simba!

473
00:24:28,594 --> 00:24:30,762
辛巴，我对你非常失望
Simba, I'm very disappointed in you.

474
00:24:30,804 --> 00:24:33,265
我知道
- I know. - You could've been killed.

475
00:24:33,307 --> 00:24:35,100
你可能会死掉
You deliberately disobeyed me...

476
00:24:35,142 --> 00:24:37,728
你故意违抗我的命令
and what's worse, you put Nala in danger.

477
00:24:35,556 --> 00:24:36,454
而且更糟的是

478
00:24:36,624 --> 00:24:39,491
你和娜娜有生命危险

479
00:24:38,937 --> 00:24:41,773
我只是想要跟你一样勇敢
I was just trying to be brave, like you.

480
00:24:41,815 --> 00:24:45,152
我只有在必要的时候才勇敢
I'm only brave when I have to be.

481
00:24:45,194 --> 00:24:48,906
辛巴
Simba, being brave...

482
00:24:48,947 --> 00:24:51,366
勇敢并不表示你要去找麻烦
doesn't mean you go looking for trouble.

483
00:24:51,408 --> 00:24:53,368
可是你好像什么都不怕
But you're not scared of anything.

484
00:24:54,578 --> 00:24:55,746
我今天就怕了
I was today.

485
00:24:55,787 --> 00:24:57,998
真的？
- You were? - Yes.

486
00:24:58,040 --> 00:25:00,209
是的
I thought I might lose you.

487
00:24:58,546 --> 00:25:00,514
我怕我会失去你

488
00:25:00,250 --> 00:25:04,296
噢...原来国王也会害怕
Oh. I guess even kings get scared, huh?

489
00:25:05,589 --> 00:25:07,883
但是你知道吗？
- But you know what? - What?

490
00:25:07,925 --> 00:25:10,511
什么？
I think those hyenas were even scareder.

491
00:25:08,456 --> 00:25:10,822
我认为那些土狼比你还害怕

492
00:25:12,095 --> 00:25:15,265
哈...
'Cause nobody messes with your dad.

493
00:25:12,961 --> 00:25:16,089
因为没有人有胆子敢惹你爸爸

494
00:25:15,307 --> 00:25:17,768
过来
- Come here, you. - Oh, no! No!

495
00:25:17,098 --> 00:25:18,156
不要，不要

496
00:25:18,299 --> 00:25:20,733
放手啦！

497
00:25:20,103 --> 00:25:21,396
来呀！
Aah! Come here!

498
00:25:23,815 --> 00:25:25,025
Gotcha!

499
00:25:30,280 --> 00:25:31,865
爸
Dad?

500
00:25:31,907 --> 00:25:33,242
嗯
We're pals, right?

501
00:25:33,283 --> 00:25:34,701
我们是不是伙伴
Right.

502
00:25:34,743 --> 00:25:37,496
对
And we'll always be together, right?

503
00:25:35,283 --> 00:25:38,582
那我们就永远在一起，对吧

504
00:25:38,789 --> 00:25:41,667
辛巴
Simba, let me tell you something...

505
00:25:41,708 --> 00:25:44,461
我告诉你一些 我爸爸以前跟我说的话
that my father told me.

506
00:25:44,545 --> 00:25:46,505
你看那些星星
Look at the stars.

507
00:25:46,547 --> 00:25:48,966
过去那些伟大的君王
The great kings of the past...

508
00:25:48,966 --> 00:25:51,593
从那些星星上看着我们
look down on us from those stars.

509
00:25:51,635 --> 00:25:53,971
真的？
- Really? - Yes.

510
00:25:54,012 --> 00:25:56,431
是呀
So, whenever you feel alone...

511
00:25:54,869 --> 00:25:57,133
所以每当你寂寞的时候

512
00:25:56,473 --> 00:25:58,767
要记得那些君王 永远在那里指引着你
just remember that those kings...

513
00:25:58,809 --> 00:26:02,688
will always be there to guide you...

514
00:26:02,729 --> 00:26:04,147
还有我也是
and so will I.

515
00:26:10,946 --> 00:26:12,781
木法沙真差劲
Man, that lousy Mufasa.

516
00:26:12,823 --> 00:26:14,616
害我一个星期都不能坐
I won't be able to sit for a week.

517
00:26:18,162 --> 00:26:19,788
这个不好笑，阿德
It's not funny, Ed.

518
00:26:23,542 --> 00:26:24,751
闭嘴！
Hey, shut up!

519
00:26:28,505 --> 00:26:30,215
你们安静一点好不好？
Will you knock it off?

520
00:26:30,257 --> 00:26:32,885
Well, he started it.

521
00:26:32,926 --> 00:26:35,679
是他先开始的
Look at you guys. No wonder we're dangling...

522
00:26:33,741 --> 00:26:34,935
看看你们俩个

523
00:26:35,721 --> 00:26:37,181
难怪我们会在 食物链最底部晃荡
at the bottom of the food chain.

524
00:26:37,222 --> 00:26:38,765
我痛恨晃荡
Man, I hate dangling.

525
00:26:38,807 --> 00:26:41,226
废话！
Yeah? You know, if it weren't for those lions...

526
00:26:41,268 --> 00:26:42,728
如果不是那些狮子 这地方早就是我们的了
we'd be runnin' the joint.

527
00:26:42,769 --> 00:26:44,229
我痛恨狮子！
Man, I hate lions.

528
00:26:44,271 --> 00:26:45,856
那么顽固
- So pushy. - And hairy.

529
00:26:45,898 --> 00:26:48,066
又毛茸茸的
- And stinky. - And, man, are they...

530
00:26:46,454 --> 00:26:47,148
而且又臭

531
00:26:48,108 --> 00:26:50,152
还有老天他们...
U-u-u-ugly!

532
00:26:49,857 --> 00:26:51,757
丑死了

533
00:26:51,486 --> 00:26:55,365
我们狮子当然 不全都是那么糟糕的
Oh, surely, we lions are not all that bad.

534
00:26:55,365 --> 00:26:58,243
Oh, Scar. It's just you.

535
00:26:58,285 --> 00:27:00,412
刀疤，原来是你
We were afraid it was somebody important.

536
00:27:00,454 --> 00:27:01,914
我们还以为是什么大人物呢！
Yeah, you know, like Mufasa.

537
00:27:01,955 --> 00:27:03,582
对呀，就像木法沙
- Yeah. - I see.

538
00:27:03,624 --> 00:27:06,043
是呀
- Now, that's power. - Tell me about it.

539
00:27:03,104 --> 00:27:03,866
是吗？

540
00:27:04,005 --> 00:27:05,233
那才叫力量

541
00:27:06,043 --> 00:27:08,170
一点也没错 光听他的名字我就会发抖
I just hear that name and I shudder.

542
00:27:08,212 --> 00:27:10,380
木法沙
- Mufasa! - Ooh! Do it again.

543
00:27:10,422 --> 00:27:11,882
再来一次
Mufasa!

544
00:27:11,882 --> 00:27:13,050
木法沙
Mufasa! Mufasa! Mufasa!

545
00:27:12,747 --> 00:27:14,772
木法沙...

546
00:27:14,593 --> 00:27:16,345
真过瘾
Ooh, it tingles.

547
00:27:16,386 --> 00:27:19,306
我身边全是一些白痴
I'm surrounded by idiots.

548
00:27:19,348 --> 00:27:21,141
得了吧，刀疤
Now, you, Scar, I mean, you're one of us.

549
00:27:21,183 --> 00:27:22,518
你是我们的一份子
You're our pal.

550
00:27:22,559 --> 00:27:23,727
别忘了你是我们的伙伴
Charmed.

551
00:27:23,769 --> 00:27:25,187
真感人...
Oh, I like that.

552
00:27:25,229 --> 00:27:27,856
噢，我喜欢
He's not king, but he's still so proper.

553
00:27:25,726 --> 00:27:28,354
他不是国王 但他还是那么有威严

554
00:27:27,898 --> 00:27:30,901
是呀，刀疤
Did you bring us anything to eat, Scar, old buddy?

555
00:27:30,943 --> 00:27:32,110
你带什么给我们吃的
Did ya, did ya, did ya?

556
00:27:32,152 --> 00:27:34,571
嘿，老伙伴，好兄弟
I don't think you really deserve this.

557
00:27:31,666 --> 00:27:32,496
有没有，有没有

558
00:27:32,667 --> 00:27:34,828
我认为你们实在不值得

559
00:27:34,613 --> 00:27:37,699
我是特别把那些小狮子 送来给你们的
I practically gift-wrapped those cubs for you...

560
00:27:37,741 --> 00:27:41,203
而你们却让他给跑掉了
and you couldn't even dispose of them.

561
00:27:43,789 --> 00:27:44,915
可是你知道
Well, you know...

562
00:27:44,957 --> 00:27:47,876
他们并不是 自己单独来的，刀疤
it wasn't exactly like they were alone, Scar.

563
00:27:47,918 --> 00:27:50,170
对呀！我们该怎么做呢？
Yeah. What were we supposed to do...

564
00:27:50,212 --> 00:27:52,047
杀了木法沙？
kill Mufasa?

565
00:27:53,465 --> 00:27:55,717
一点也没错
Precisely.

566
00:27:55,759 --> 00:27:57,052
Huh?

567
00:28:06,144 --> 00:28:10,190
不要在我面前耍威风
* I know that your powers of retention *

568
00:28:10,232 --> 00:28:13,986
仔细看 像个饭桶不中用
* Are as wet as a warthog's backside *

569
00:28:14,027 --> 00:28:16,071
你给我站好 仔细听着
* But thick as you are *

570
00:28:16,113 --> 00:28:18,240
* Pay attention *

571
00:28:18,282 --> 00:28:22,077
我的话已经够明白
* My words are a matter of pride *

572
00:28:22,119 --> 00:28:25,873
那是所谓无言的表白
* It's clear from your vacant expressions *

573
00:28:25,914 --> 00:28:29,877
这地方由我来主宰
* The lights are not all on upstairs *

574
00:28:29,918 --> 00:28:33,380
难道你们都没有发现
* But we're talking kings and successions *

575
00:28:33,422 --> 00:28:36,175
王位继承权在我手中
* Even you can't be caught unawares *

576
00:28:37,801 --> 00:28:41,138
准备好你的心静静等候
* So prepare for the chance of a lifetime *

577
00:28:41,180 --> 00:28:45,642
迎接这一个天大消息
* Be prepared for sensational news *

578
00:28:45,684 --> 00:28:49,438
一个新的时代它悄悄要到来
* A shiny new era is tiptoeing nearer *

579
00:28:49,479 --> 00:28:51,148
那我们又算什么？
* And where do we feature? *

580
00:28:51,190 --> 00:28:53,442
不管我多恶毒
* Just listen to teacher *

581
00:28:53,483 --> 00:28:55,402
只要听我吩咐 不要再犯错误
* I know it sounds sordid *

582
00:28:55,444 --> 00:28:57,446
* But you'll be rewarded *

583
00:28:57,487 --> 00:29:00,949
以后总会有你的好处
* When at last I am given my dues *

584
00:29:00,991 --> 00:29:04,786
我要大声地向你宣布
* And injustice deliciously squared *

585
00:29:04,828 --> 00:29:08,081
快准备
* Be prepared *

586
00:29:08,123 --> 00:29:09,416
不对！还有的呢！
Yeah, be prepared.

587
00:29:09,458 --> 00:29:12,085
我们会准备的
We'll be prepared. For what?

588
00:29:12,127 --> 00:29:13,462
准备什么？
For the death of the king.

589
00:29:13,504 --> 00:29:14,880
准备木法沙王之死！
Why, is he sick?

590
00:29:14,922 --> 00:29:16,173
怎么了？他病了？ 不
No, fool, we're going to kill him...

591
00:29:16,215 --> 00:29:17,674
笨蛋！我们要杀了他 还有辛巴
and Simba, too.

592
00:29:17,716 --> 00:29:19,384
好主意 谁需要国王啊！
Great idea. Who needs a king?

593
00:29:19,426 --> 00:29:22,262
不要王......
* No king, no king, la-la la-la la la *

594
00:29:22,304 --> 00:29:24,431
啦......
Idiots! There will be a king!

595
00:29:22,676 --> 00:29:24,735
白痴！还会有另外一个王的

596
00:29:24,473 --> 00:29:27,518
但是你自己说......
- Hey, but you said... - I will be king!

597
00:29:25,780 --> 00:29:28,010
我将要做你们的王

598
00:29:27,559 --> 00:29:33,273
只要跟着我
Stick with me, and you'll never go hungry again.

599
00:29:29,950 --> 00:29:33,545
你们就再也不会饿肚子了

600
00:29:33,315 --> 00:29:34,650
好耶！
- Yeah! - Yeah! All right!

601
00:29:34,691 --> 00:29:36,193
国王万岁！
All right! Long live the king!

602
00:29:36,235 --> 00:29:37,611
国王万岁！
Long live the king!

603
00:29:37,653 --> 00:29:39,196
Long live the king!

604
00:29:39,238 --> 00:29:40,989
国王万岁！
* King, king, king, king, king, king, king *

605
00:29:41,031 --> 00:29:44,326
看来很快就会有依靠
* It's great that we'll soon be connected *

606
00:29:44,368 --> 00:29:48,622
随时随地伺候你左右
* With a king who'll be all-time adored *

607
00:29:48,664 --> 00:29:50,332
要投靠我 不要怀疑
* Of course, quid pro quo *

608
00:29:50,374 --> 00:29:52,209
* You're expected *

609
00:29:52,251 --> 00:29:56,296
保证大家都会好过
* To take certain duties on board *

610
00:29:56,338 --> 00:30:00,133
看来未来是充满着希望
* The future is littered with prizes *

611
00:30:00,175 --> 00:30:04,638
保证过就不会泡汤
* And though I'm the main addressee *

612
00:30:04,680 --> 00:30:08,016
让我再一次向你提醒
* The point that I must emphasize is *

613
00:30:08,058 --> 00:30:10,435
我就是你唯一靠山
* You won't get a sniff without me *

614
00:30:12,020 --> 00:30:15,649
快准备！
* So prepare for the coup of the century *

615
00:30:13,527 --> 00:30:15,995
这计划前所未有

616
00:30:15,691 --> 00:30:18,569
这计划只要你帮一帮
* Be prepared for the murkiest scam *

617
00:30:18,610 --> 00:30:20,028
* La la la *

618
00:30:20,070 --> 00:30:21,864
这周详的计划 是万无一失的
* Meticulous planning *

619
00:30:21,905 --> 00:30:23,866
* Tenacity spanning *

620
00:30:23,907 --> 00:30:25,993
是难得一见的 是不能否认的
* Decades of denial *

621
00:30:26,034 --> 00:30:29,705
* Is simply why I'll be king undisputed *

622
00:30:29,746 --> 00:30:31,748
不能抵抗 又雄壮威严受尊敬的我
* Respected, saluted *

623
00:30:31,790 --> 00:30:35,210
就是森林之王
* And seen for the wonder I am *

624
00:30:35,252 --> 00:30:39,047
因为我要的理想更高
* Yes, my teeth and ambitions are bared *

625
00:30:39,089 --> 00:30:43,427
快准备
* Be prepared *

626
00:30:43,468 --> 00:30:46,847
因为我要的理想更高
* Yes, our teeth and ambitions are bared *

627
00:30:46,889 --> 00:30:50,893
快准备
* Be prepared *

628
00:31:02,946 --> 00:31:04,281
好，你在这等着
Now, you wait here.

629
00:31:04,406 --> 00:31:07,659
你爸爸为你准备了一个大惊喜
Your father has a marvelous surprise for you.

630
00:31:07,701 --> 00:31:09,036
什么惊喜？
Ooh, what is it?

631
00:31:09,077 --> 00:31:12,247
如果我告诉你的话 那就不叫惊喜了，对不对
If I told you, it wouldn't be a surprise.

632
00:31:12,289 --> 00:31:14,291
如果你告诉我 我会装得很惊讶
If you tell me, I'll still act surprised.

633
00:31:14,416 --> 00:31:18,295
You are such a naughty boy.

634
00:31:16,156 --> 00:31:18,886
你实在是非常的调皮

635
00:31:18,295 --> 00:31:19,713
说嘛！刀疤叔叔
Come on, Uncle Scar.

636
00:31:19,755 --> 00:31:21,548
不......
No, no, no, no, no.

637
00:31:21,590 --> 00:31:23,926
这是你爸爸跟你之间的事情
This is just for you and your daddy.

638
00:31:23,967 --> 00:31:28,722
是那种父子之间的...关系
You know, a sort of father-son... thing.

639
00:31:28,764 --> 00:31:31,600
好了，我最好去找他去
Well, I better go get him.

640
00:31:31,642 --> 00:31:34,895
我跟你一起去
- I'll go with you. - No!

641
00:31:33,073 --> 00:31:34,665
不！

642
00:31:34,937 --> 00:31:38,690
不...你只管待在这个石块上
No. Just stay on this rock.

643
00:31:38,732 --> 00:31:40,859
你不会想像上次那样 再遇到土狼吧？
You wouldn't want to end up in another mess...

644
00:31:40,901 --> 00:31:42,611
like you did with the hyenas.

645
00:31:42,653 --> 00:31:43,987
你知道那件事呀？
You know about that?

646
00:31:44,029 --> 00:31:46,490
辛巴，每个人都知道那件事
Simba, everybody knows about that.

647
00:31:46,490 --> 00:31:49,117
真的吗？
- Really? - Oh, yes.

648
00:31:49,159 --> 00:31:52,955
是啊，算你幸运
Lucky Daddy was there to save you, eh?

649
00:31:51,391 --> 00:31:54,258
爸爸赶去救你了，对不对啊？

650
00:31:52,996 --> 00:31:55,749
Oh, and just between us...

651
00:31:55,791 --> 00:31:59,211
这是我们的小秘密
you might want to work on that little roar of yours.

652
00:31:56,763 --> 00:31:59,857
你是不是该练习练习 你的吼叫声了呢？

653
00:31:59,253 --> 00:32:01,880
哦，好吧
Oh, OK.

654
00:32:03,757 --> 00:32:07,469
嘿！刀疤叔叔
Hey, Uncle Scar, will I like this surprise?

655
00:32:07,511 --> 00:32:11,807
我会喜欢那个惊喜吗？
Simba, it's to die for.

656
00:32:08,508 --> 00:32:13,275
辛巴，你会喜欢死的

657
00:32:32,870 --> 00:32:35,622
闭嘴！
- Shut up. - I can't help it.

658
00:32:35,664 --> 00:32:38,083
我也没办法 我肚子好饿
I'm so hungry. I got to have a wildebeest.

659
00:32:38,125 --> 00:32:39,626
我可以吃下一头野牛
Stay put.

660
00:32:39,668 --> 00:32:41,920
不要乱动
Can't I just pick off one of the little sick ones?

661
00:32:40,340 --> 00:32:41,034
拜托！

662
00:32:41,962 --> 00:32:45,924
我可不可以 吃一头生病的就好了
No. We wait for the signal from Scar.

663
00:32:42,776 --> 00:32:47,270
不行！我们要等待刀疤的讯号

664
00:32:47,593 --> 00:32:51,346
他在那边
There he is. Let's go.

665
00:32:49,650 --> 00:32:51,914
我们走

666
00:32:51,388 --> 00:32:54,391
吼叫声
Little roar. Puhh.

667
00:33:55,285 --> 00:33:58,330
陛下，你看！ 有东西在移动
Oh, look, sire, the herd is on the move.

668
00:33:58,372 --> 00:34:00,332
奇怪？
- Odd. - Mufasa, quick!

669
00:34:00,374 --> 00:34:02,543
木法沙！快点 动物逃窜
Stampede in the gorge.

670
00:34:02,584 --> 00:34:05,254
在峡谷那儿 而辛巴也在
- Simba's down there. - Simba?

671
00:34:04,958 --> 00:34:06,482
辛巴？

672
00:34:27,317 --> 00:34:28,944
沙祖！救我
Zazu, help me!

673
00:34:28,986 --> 00:34:31,029
你爸爸已经来了
Your father is on the way! Hold on!

674
00:34:31,071 --> 00:34:32,281
撑着点
Hurry!

675
00:34:32,052 --> 00:34:33,952
快呀...

676
00:34:35,701 --> 00:34:38,453
那边，在那儿
There, on that tree.

677
00:34:38,495 --> 00:34:39,788
在那树上
Hold on, Simba!

678
00:34:39,059 --> 00:34:41,960
捉好，辛巴

679
00:34:46,712 --> 00:34:50,465
刀疤，这太可怕了
Oh, Scar, this is awful! What'll we do?

680
00:34:50,507 --> 00:34:52,301
我们该怎么办？
Ha! I'll go back to help, that's what I'll do.

681
00:34:50,270 --> 00:34:51,794
我该做些什么？

682
00:34:52,342 --> 00:34:53,635
我回去搬救兵
I'll go back... Oof!

683
00:34:52,806 --> 00:34:55,400
我就这么做 我去搬救...

684
00:35:29,046 --> 00:35:30,547
爸...
Dad!

685
00:35:53,403 --> 00:35:55,280
刀疤...
Scar!

686
00:35:55,322 --> 00:35:58,784
Uhh! Brother! Help me!

687
00:35:57,404 --> 00:36:00,305
弟弟，救救我

688
00:36:06,917 --> 00:36:10,420
愿国王万岁
Long live the king.

689
00:36:13,924 --> 00:36:19,555
No!

690
00:36:17,657 --> 00:36:20,057
不...

691
00:36:31,275 --> 00:36:32,901
爸...
Dad!

692
00:36:43,996 --> 00:36:45,956
Dad?

693
00:36:45,618 --> 00:36:46,380
爸

694
00:37:23,452 --> 00:37:25,662
爸
Dad?

695
00:37:25,704 --> 00:37:28,874
爸，起来
Dad, come on.

696
00:37:28,916 --> 00:37:31,835
你一定要起来
You got to get up.

697
00:37:31,835 --> 00:37:33,962
爸...
Dad?

698
00:37:34,004 --> 00:37:35,881
跟我回家啦
We got to go home.

699
00:37:46,683 --> 00:37:50,979
救命啊...
Help!

700
00:37:51,021 --> 00:37:53,524
有没有人？
Somebody!

701
00:37:53,565 --> 00:37:55,400
任何人...
Anybody.

702
00:37:56,819 --> 00:37:59,905
救命
Help.

703
00:38:29,059 --> 00:38:30,894
辛巴
Simba.

704
00:38:30,936 --> 00:38:32,896
看你弄得...
What have you done?

705
00:38:34,106 --> 00:38:37,359
有好多动物 他想救我
There were wildebeests, and he tried to save me.

706
00:38:37,401 --> 00:38:40,696
这真的是意外 我不是故意的
It was an accident. I didn't mean for it to happen.

707
00:38:40,737 --> 00:38:44,950
当然，你当然不是故意的
Of course, of course you didn't.

708
00:38:44,992 --> 00:38:49,955
没有人会故意 要让这种事发生的
No one ever means for these things to happen...

709
00:38:49,997 --> 00:38:52,332
但是国王已经死了
but the king is dead.

710
00:38:53,876 --> 00:38:56,962
而且，如果不是因为你 他现在还会活着的
And if it weren't for you, he'd still be alive.

711
00:39:01,675 --> 00:39:04,344
你妈妈会怎么想呢？
What will your mother think?

712
00:39:04,386 --> 00:39:06,889
What am I going to do?

713
00:39:06,930 --> 00:39:08,265
那我该怎么办？
Run away, Simba.

714
00:39:07,426 --> 00:39:10,088
跑的远远的，辛巴

715
00:39:09,641 --> 00:39:14,771
快跑
Run. Run away and never return.

716
00:39:10,963 --> 00:39:15,161
跑的远远的再也不要回来了

717
00:39:20,777 --> 00:39:22,988
杀了他
Kill him.

718
00:40:14,998 --> 00:40:17,793
Hey, there he goes. There he goes.

719
00:40:17,835 --> 00:40:19,837
他在那边 往那边跑了
So, go get him.

720
00:40:19,837 --> 00:40:21,463
那就快追呀
There ain't no way I'm going in there.

721
00:40:21,505 --> 00:40:25,300
我才不愿意到那边去呢！
You want me to come out looking like you, cactus butt?

722
00:40:22,167 --> 00:40:22,861
怎么？

723
00:40:22,968 --> 00:40:26,927
你想要我跟你一样 变成个仙人掌啊？

724
00:40:26,552 --> 00:40:27,803
我们一定得完成任务
But we got to finish the job.

725
00:40:27,845 --> 00:40:30,973
唉！反正他出去以后 就完蛋定了
Well, he's as good as dead out there anyway.

726
00:40:31,014 --> 00:40:33,308
如果他回来的话 我们再杀他
And if he comes back, we'll kill him.

727
00:40:33,350 --> 00:40:35,477
对！你听到没有？
Yeah! You hear that?

728
00:40:35,519 --> 00:40:39,273
如果你敢回来 我们就杀了你
If you ever come back, we'll kill you!

729
00:40:48,073 --> 00:40:51,910
木法沙的死亡是个可怕的悲剧
Mufasa's death is a terrible tragedy...

730
00:40:51,994 --> 00:40:56,331
但是辛巴几乎才开始他的生命 竟然也...
but to lose Simba, who had barely begun to live...

731
00:40:56,373 --> 00:41:02,337
For me, it is a deep, personal loss.

732
00:40:58,020 --> 00:41:02,719
对我来说 这是一个极大的个人损失

733
00:41:02,379 --> 00:41:04,047
我在极悲恸的心情下登上王位
So, it is with a heavy heart...

734
00:41:04,089 --> 00:41:06,341
that I assume the throne.

735
00:41:06,383 --> 00:41:09,052
但是我们 必须振作起来忘掉悲痛
Yet out of the ashes of this tragedy...

736
00:41:09,094 --> 00:41:13,682
we shall rise to greet the dawning of a new era...

737
00:41:11,167 --> 00:41:14,398
共同迎接一个崭新时代的来临

738
00:41:13,724 --> 00:41:17,561
我们狮子将跟土狼 一起走向光明伟大的未来
in which lion and hyena come together...

739
00:41:17,603 --> 00:41:21,940
in a great and glorious future.

740
00:42:08,028 --> 00:42:11,365
Get out! Get out! Get out of here!

741
00:42:09,775 --> 00:42:10,969
走开一走开

742
00:42:11,406 --> 00:42:13,742
快走开
I love this! Bowling for buzzards.

743
00:42:12,010 --> 00:42:15,741
我喜欢赶走秃鹰

744
00:42:13,784 --> 00:42:16,411
Gets 'em every time.

745
00:42:15,881 --> 00:42:18,543
每次都成功

746
00:42:17,704 --> 00:42:21,583
Uh-oh. Hey, Timon, you better come look.

747
00:42:20,085 --> 00:42:21,985
丁满，你最好过来看看

748
00:42:21,625 --> 00:42:23,669
我看他好像还活着
I think it's still alive.

749
00:42:25,295 --> 00:42:28,340
哎哟！这什么东西呀？
All righty, what have we got here?

750
00:42:34,429 --> 00:42:37,850
天啊！是只狮子
Jeez, it's a lion! Run, Pumbaa, move it!

751
00:42:37,891 --> 00:42:41,186
彭彭，快跑
Hey, Timon, it's just a little lion.

752
00:42:38,837 --> 00:42:42,898
丁满，他只是只小狮子

753
00:42:41,228 --> 00:42:45,774
Look at him. He's so cute and all alone.

754
00:42:43,041 --> 00:42:44,599
你看他那么可爱

755
00:42:45,816 --> 00:42:48,318
而且是一个人 我们能留下他吗？
- Can we keep him? - Pumbaa, are you nuts?

756
00:42:48,360 --> 00:42:51,613
彭彭，你疯了吗？
You're talking about a lion. Lions eat guys like us.

757
00:42:48,947 --> 00:42:50,244
躺在这儿的是只狮子

758
00:42:51,655 --> 00:42:54,199
狮子就是专门吃我们的
- But he's so little. - He'll get bigger.

759
00:42:54,241 --> 00:42:55,534
但是他还那么小
Maybe he'll be on our side.

760
00:42:53,619 --> 00:42:54,608
他以后会长大的

761
00:42:55,576 --> 00:42:58,328
也许他会变得跟我们一国
Ha! That's the stupidest thing I ever heard.

762
00:42:58,370 --> 00:43:01,498
这是我听过最蠢的话了
Maybe he'll... Hey, I got it.

763
00:42:58,957 --> 00:42:59,924
或许他会...

764
00:43:01,540 --> 00:43:02,958
咦...我有点子了
What if he's on our side?

765
00:43:03,000 --> 00:43:06,295
如果他跟我们一国
Having a lion around might not be such a bad idea.

766
00:43:03,762 --> 00:43:06,663
有只狮子在身边或许蛮不错的

767
00:43:06,336 --> 00:43:07,504
那我们就留下他罗
So, we're keeping him?

768
00:43:07,546 --> 00:43:09,840
当然，这里是谁做主啊？
Pbbt! Of course. Who's the brains of this outfit?

769
00:43:09,882 --> 00:43:11,550
我认为他应该留下
- Uh... - My point exactly.

770
00:43:11,592 --> 00:43:12,968
哎哟！天啊！我热死了
Jeez, I'm fried.

771
00:43:13,010 --> 00:43:14,887
我们快离开这儿 找个阴凉的地方
Let's get out of here and find some shade.

772
00:43:23,437 --> 00:43:25,731
你还好吧？孩子
- You OK, kid? - I guess so.

773
00:43:25,772 --> 00:43:28,150
我想是吧
- You nearly died. - I saved you.

774
00:43:26,251 --> 00:43:27,377
你差点就死了

775
00:43:28,192 --> 00:43:30,986
我救了你
Well, Pumbaa helped... a little.

776
00:43:29,354 --> 00:43:31,345
彭彭也帮了...一滴滴忙

777
00:43:31,028 --> 00:43:32,905
谢谢你们帮忙
Thanks for your help.

778
00:43:34,072 --> 00:43:37,659
你要去哪里？
- Hey, where you going? - Nowhere.

779
00:43:35,827 --> 00:43:38,022
不知道

780
00:43:37,701 --> 00:43:39,203
他看起来很BLUE
Gee, he looks blue.

781
00:43:39,203 --> 00:43:41,205
我倒觉得是金黄色
I'd say brownish gold.

782
00:43:41,246 --> 00:43:42,789
不，我是说一沮丧
No, no, no. I mean he's depressed.

783
00:43:42,873 --> 00:43:44,333
Oh.

784
00:43:44,374 --> 00:43:46,168
孩子你在烦什么？
Kid, what's eating you?

785
00:43:46,210 --> 00:43:48,170
烦？狮子可是万兽之王
Nothing. He's at the top of the food chain.

786
00:43:51,715 --> 00:43:54,760
烦个屁呀！
The food chain!

787
00:43:56,887 --> 00:43:58,722
那你从哪儿来的？
So, where you from?

788
00:43:58,764 --> 00:44:00,849
谁在乎？我又不能回去
Who cares? I can't go back.

789
00:44:00,891 --> 00:44:03,018
你是被扫地出门的
Ah, you're an outcast.

790
00:44:03,060 --> 00:44:04,394
好极了！我们也是
That's great. So are we.

791
00:44:04,436 --> 00:44:05,604
你做了什么事？
What'd you do, kid?

792
00:44:05,646 --> 00:44:06,939
很可怕的事 但是我不想跟你们说
Something terrible...

793
00:44:06,980 --> 00:44:08,440
but I don't want to talk about it.

794
00:44:08,482 --> 00:44:10,025
很好，我们也不想听
Good. We don't want to hear about it.

795
00:44:10,067 --> 00:44:12,277
拜托，丁满 我们能帮忙吗？
Come on, Timon. Anything we can do?

796
00:44:12,319 --> 00:44:15,030
除非你们能够改变历史
Not unless you can change the past.

797
00:44:15,072 --> 00:44:18,367
孩子你要知道在这个时候 我这位伙伴丁满说
Kid, in times like this, my buddy Timon says...

798
00:44:18,408 --> 00:44:20,953
你必须把你的背后抛到过去
you got to put your behind in your past.

799
00:44:20,994 --> 00:44:23,872
不...
No, no, no. Amateur.

800
00:44:23,914 --> 00:44:26,708
我是说... 笨蛋
Lie down before you hurt yourself.

801
00:44:24,576 --> 00:44:27,010
能不能闭上你的乌鸦嘴呀

802
00:44:26,750 --> 00:44:29,461
